high_descs: Turn right and walk over to the counter, then turn left to face the counter.
Pick up the butter knife off of the counter.
Turn left and walk over to the sink.
Put the butter knife in the sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn off the water and remove the now clean butter knife.
Turn left and walk over to the counter.
Open the third drawer from the top to the left of the dish washer and put the clean butter knife inside then close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean butter knife in a drawer.

high_descs: Turn right, move to the counter right of the sink.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Bring the knife to the sink on the left.
Wash the knife in the sink with water.
Bring the knife to the left, to the drawer left of the dishwasher.
Open the drawer left of dishwasher and put the cleaned knife in there.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned knife in a drawer.

high_descs: move to the counter to the right of the sink
pick up a knife from the counter
move to the sink to the left
clean the knife in the sink
move to the counter to the left of the dishwasher
put the knife in the drawer to the left of the dishwasher
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned knife in a drawer.
